casebody.data:
No. 108,

Orig.

Nebraska v. Wyoming et al. [For earlier decision herein, see, e. g., ante, p. 584.]

State of Nebraska’s Motion for Leave to File Amended Petition for an Apportionment of Non-Irrigation Season Flows and for the Assertion of New Claims denied without prejudice with respect to Count I. The Special Master is directed to provide a recommendation to the Court as to whether the motion for leave to file an amended petition should be granted with respect to Counts II and III.
